                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060521-52-defend516 t18060521-52-punish277"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
